*** Settings ***
Documentation      Login test suite for {{projectName}}.
...                Covers smoke + negative + data-driven scenarios.
Resource           ../resources/common.resource
Resource           ../resources/pages/LoginPage.resource
Resource           ../resources/pages/HomePage.resource
Suite Setup        Open Browser To Login Page
Suite Teardown     Close Browser Session
Test Teardown      Take Screenshot On Failure

Force Tags         login

*** Test Cases ***
Valid Login Should Redirect To Inventory
    [Documentation]    Happy path — valid credentials land on the inventory page.
    [Tags]             smoke
    Navigate To Login Page
    Login With Credentials    ${USERNAME}    ${PASSWORD}
    Verify Successful Login

Invalid Login Should Show Error
    [Documentation]    Wrong credentials surface the error banner.
    [Tags]             regression    negative
    Navigate To Login Page
    Login With Credentials    invalid_user    wrong_password
    Wait Until Element Is Visible    ${ERROR_MESSAGE}    ${TIMEOUT}
    Element Should Be Visible        ${ERROR_MESSAGE}

Empty Username Should Show Error
    [Documentation]    Empty username surfaces the error banner.
    [Tags]             regression    negative
    Navigate To Login Page
    Login With Credentials    ${EMPTY}    ${PASSWORD}
    Wait Until Element Is Visible    ${ERROR_MESSAGE}    ${TIMEOUT}
    Element Should Be Visible        ${ERROR_MESSAGE}

Empty Password Should Show Error
    [Documentation]    Empty password surfaces the error banner.
    [Tags]             regression    negative
    Navigate To Login Page
    Login With Credentials    ${USERNAME}    ${EMPTY}
    Wait Until Element Is Visible    ${ERROR_MESSAGE}    ${TIMEOUT}
    Element Should Be Visible        ${ERROR_MESSAGE}

{{#if utilities.dataProvider}}
Data-Driven Login Scenarios
    [Documentation]    Drive the login flow from a list of scenarios.
    [Tags]             regression    data-driven
    [Template]         Verify Login Outcome
    ${USERNAME}       ${PASSWORD}         success
    invalid_user      ${PASSWORD}         failure
    ${USERNAME}       wrong_password      failure
    ${EMPTY}          ${PASSWORD}         failure
    ${USERNAME}       ${EMPTY}            failure
{{/if}}

*** Keywords ***
Verify Login Outcome
    [Documentation]    Helper for the Data-Driven scenarios above.
    [Arguments]    ${username}    ${password}    ${expected}
    Navigate To Login Page
    Login With Credentials    ${username}    ${password}
    IF    '${expected}' == 'success'
        Verify Successful Login
    ELSE
        Wait Until Element Is Visible    ${ERROR_MESSAGE}    ${TIMEOUT}
        Element Should Be Visible        ${ERROR_MESSAGE}
    END
